overview: We are one of the largest manufacturer of prototypes and small-volume PCB in China. Founded in 1999, We are committed to serve domestic and foreign high-tech enterprises and research institutes. Under the guidance of its business philosophy,”market-oriented, quality-centric”, We are becoming a leading general solutions provider of hardware design outsourcing, including PCB design, PCB manufacture and SMT mounting services. We are making every effort to build a value chain system which is customer-oriented and adds value to all our customer relationships.
